' on the 3rd floor of the paladin guild hall.  Same structure as Torsten Reidan**<br>You begin tracking A File Cabinet.<br>You say, 'Hail, A File Cabinet'<br>A File Cabinet scowls at you, ready to attack -- You could probably win this fight.<br>You begin to hide...<br>A File Cabinet regards you indifferently -- You could probably win this fight.<br><br>**Give the file cabinet the new records while invised.**<br>**If not invised you will get this message**<br>**A File Cabinet says 'I will do nothing to aid beings like you.'**<br>**You will lose the records and have to get another one**<br><br>A File Cabinet slams shut after you take the old file out.<br>Guard Hargrar spawns and says 'Hey! What are you doing in there?!'<br>Guard Hargrar scowls at you, ready to attack -- he appears to be quite formidable.<br>You have been summoned!<br>**Con's Blue to lvl 51 and I assume he's 50 cause he summons.  You do not need to kill him, just run to the zone to clear agro. BTW, you won't get add's as he's on no faction table**<br>You have slain Guard Hargrar!<br>You gain party experience!!<br><br>You begin tracking Euzan Jurek.<br>**give Euzan Jurek the old records you received from the file cabinet and the Insignia Earring of Veracity**<br><br>Euzan Jurek says 'By now you must realize that we need to avoid the question because of whom we are.  Seru is not the Noble Paladin this city would have you believe.  You see they teach that Katta feared Seru and that he had faked his own poisoning so they could pin the blame on Seru.  The next thing that I ask of you, I ask because you can travel without question from one city to another.  Go to Katta and give this report  to Tilbok Furrunner.  Tell him we are successfully rooted within Sanctus Seru and await any commands.'<br>Your faction standing with Validus Custodus got better.<br>Your faction standing with Katta Castellum Citizens got better.<br>Your faction standing with Magus Conlegium got better.<br>Your faction standing with Nathyn Illuminious got worse.<br>Your faction standing with Coterie of the Eternal Night got worse.<br>Your faction standing with Seru got worse.<br>Your faction standing with Hand of Seru got worse.<br>Your faction standing with Eye of Seru got worse.<br>Your faction standing with Hand Legionnaries got worse.<br>**You recieve report and Etched Earring of Veracity**<br><br>Etched Earring of Veracity   <br>LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP  <br>Slot: EAR<br>AC: +2 Str: +2 Sta: +2 Wis: +2 Int: +2  <br>Weight: 0.1  Size: TINY<br>Classes: All Classes  <br>Races: All Races  <br><br>&nbsp;<br>Baroness Limecherry Bloodberry<br>LvL 58 Half-elf Bard -|- LvL 47 Vah Shir Warrior -|-LvL 33 Eurdite Necromancer -|-<br>11 Froglok Cleric -|- 24 Dwarf Cleric</td></tr>
