ess you are hidden). If you cannot gate, remember to click off Wolf Form before exiting the building and flee. Even if you die, you will keep the reports from File Cabinet you were asked to take back.<br><br>Go back to Euzan Jurek and give him the reports and your Insignia Earring of Veracity to receive a note to Tilbok Furrunner and your Etched Earring of Veracity.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Jul 25 09:45:39 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Archon of <a href=HTTP://www.tritonguild.com target=_new>Triton</a> <br><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27642" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27642</a></td></tr>
